<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٦ -<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَثْقَلُ شَيْءٍ فِي الْمِيزَانِ خُلُقٌ حَسَنٌ إِنَّ اللَّهَ يُبْغِضُ الْفَاحِشَ الْبَذِيءَ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>